# Task: Optimize Animations for Mobile Performance

## Overview

Adapt all animations for mobile—simpler effects, shorter durations, and reduced complexity to ensure 60fps performance on mid-range devices.

## Background

Mobile animation challenges:
- Less powerful GPUs/CPUs
- Battery consumption concerns
- Different viewing context (thumb scrolling)
- Touch interactions vs. hover

Animations should be present but optimized.

## Implementation Details

### Reduce Animation Duration

```css
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  /* Faster animations on mobile */
  :root {
    --animation-duration-fast: 0.15s;
    --animation-duration-normal: 0.25s;
    --animation-duration-slow: 0.4s;
  }

  /* Scroll animations */
  .animate-on-scroll.animate-in {
    animation-duration: 0.4s; /* vs 0.6s desktop */
  }

  /* Hover/interaction animations */
  .btn, .card {
    transition-duration: 0.15s; /* vs 0.2s desktop */
  }
}
```

### Simplify Complex Animations

```css
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  /* Disable parallax on mobile */
  .parallax {
    transform: none !important;
  }

  /* Simplify background effects */
  .hero-background::before,
  .hero-background::after {
    animation: none; /* Static gradient orbs */
    /* Or much slower animation */
    animation-duration: 40s;
  }

  /* Reduce blur (expensive on mobile) */
  .hero-background::before {
    filter: blur(60px); /* vs 100px desktop */
  }

  .site-header {
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* vs 12px desktop */
  }
}
```

### Remove Expensive Effects

```css
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  /* Remove scan lines if present */
  .scan-lines {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Remove complex shadows */
  .card {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); /* Simpler shadow */
  }

  /* Disable gradient text animation */
  .hero-title {
    animation: none;
  }
}
```

### Touch-Specific States

```css
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  /* Remove hover transforms (no hover on touch) */
  .card:hover {
    transform: none;
  }

  /* Add active states instead */
  .card:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .btn:active {
    transform: scale(0.95);
  }
}
```

### Use will-change Sparingly

```css
/* Only apply will-change where needed */
.animate-on-scroll {
  will-change: opacity, transform;
}

/* Remove after animation */
.animate-on-scroll.animate-in {
  will-change: auto;
}
```

### Reduce Stagger on Mobile

```css
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  /* Fewer stagger steps */
  .stagger-children > .animate-on-scroll:nth-child(n+4) {
    --stagger-delay: 0.3s; /* Cap earlier */
  }
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Animation durations reduced on mobile
- [ ] Complex effects simplified or removed
- [ ] No jank when scrolling
- [ ] 60fps maintained on iPhone 11 / Pixel 5 class device
- [ ] Battery drain is reasonable
- [ ] Touch states replace hover states
- [ ] prefers-reduced-motion fully respected

## Files to Modify

- `assets/css/style.scss` - Mobile animation optimizations

## Testing

- Test on actual mid-range phone
- Use Performance tab in Chrome DevTools
- Check frame rate during scroll/animations
- Test battery impact (extended session)

